programme.title: Joel Osteen S3
programme.desc: Hear the messages of hope that best-selling author, evangelist and the senior pastor of Lakewood Church in Houston, Joel Osteen is delivering in each episode. Joel's positive and encouraging speeches will allow viewers to hear God's message of hope, love and victory and be inspired to do great things in life. Joel tries to teach Biblical principles in a simple way, always highlighting the power and importance of love and positive thinking.

programme.title: Secret Lives of the Super Rich (James Bond's Superyacht & Million Dollar Meal) S1 (n°609)
programme.desc: «James Bond's Superyacht & Million Dollar Meal»Tour the LA party mansion with a pool in the entrance, a cigar room and a full-service salon. Set sail like James Bond aboard the sexy superyacht from Skyfall. Behold the million-dollar meals whipped up by a one-of-a-kind chef. Swim with the dolphins at the exclusive Hawaiian resort where celebs and royalty are regular guests. Rock out inside an antique castle made of sand and stone, but equipped with spectacular modern amenities. Meet the watch titans that are transforming the world's most expensive timepieces into one-of-a-kind custom creations. Get an exclusive tour of one of the priciest properties in all of Aspen. Take a drive in the tricked-out golf carts that cost as much as a house. And prepare to be floored by the luxurious rugs that are a favorite of the rich and famous.

programme.title: La fièvre du dollar (Baby Broker Scam) S1 (n°54)
programme.desc: «Baby Broker Scam»Kevin Cohen is an attorney who says he can make dreams come true for couples desperate for children. He promises babies ... for a hefty price. But unknown to his trusting clients, Cohen is exploiting their hopes and dreams.

programme.title: Open de Charlotte

programme.title: Inspiring Steeds
programme.desc: This month Ride from FEI Originals returns for a brand-new series, spinning more heart-warming yarns about extraordinary horsemen and women, and the steeds that empower and inspire them.
